{
  "texts": [
    "Paired encoding-decoding models trained on diverse imaging archives learn efficient data projections.",
    "Telegram packets retain only these compressed latent vectors, allowing faster transfers.Upstream, smart routing algorithms schedule traffic based on bandwidth constraints and priority status inferred through real-time deep analysis.",
    "Generative adversarial networks differentiate normal and abnormal scans.",
    "This supports streaming abnormality alerts for critical cases to minimize delays.",
    "Downstream, decompressed scans undergo multi-level assessments to enrich structured findings and prime expert review."
  ]
